&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Discord is looking to hire an Administrative Business Partner to work with our VP of Engineering. With an ever-expanding schedule and set of duties, it’s more important than ever that she has a close confidant to work with on all things big and small.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;What You&#39;ll Be Doing&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;list-2wIoMU sizeMedium-3TgKSU weightNormal-sMrqnI lineLarge-2ze3kk&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Act as a strategic business partner to our VP of Engineering, understanding her business relationships with the ability to parse out what’s important for her short-term and long-term&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Collaborate with our Engineering Chief of Staff as a project manager, assigning tasks to stakeholders with timely follow-up&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Support our VP in her day-to-day tactical needs and long-term strategic needs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Attend (almost) all meetings alongside the VP. You’ll take detailed notes and cross-team action items, making sure they are followed up on&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Schedule external and internal meetings via GMail and GCal&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Work with the travel team to book domestic and international travel, including, but not limited to: flights, lodging, transportation, visas/documentation, and ensuring passes to events (when we’re back to traveling!)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Aggregate and submit all receipts and expense reports&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Collaborate closely with other admins to make sure the senior leadership team is operating like a smooth machine&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Act as a booster and defender of the admin team and department, mentoring junior admins and assisting OKR development and follow through&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;You&#39;ll Thrive In This Role If...&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;list-2wIoMU sizeMedium-3TgKSU weightNormal-sMrqnI lineLarge-2ze3kk&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Extraordinary communication skills, both written and verbal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Extraordinary project management skills - being able to see the big picture even in the small stuff&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ability to work under pressure in a fast paced environment&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Critical thinking skills to help your executives manage their time in the most efficient + effective manner&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ability to organize, prioritize and coordinate multiple work activities and projects with strong follow through&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;High level of confidentiality, discernment and judgment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience with Asana, Notion, and Ally (or similar products)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Excellent GSuite Skills - specifically Calendar and GMail&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;3+ years work experience in an administrative support role, particularly within an engineering org&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;Bonus Points&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Prior experience working in a hyper-growth environment&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Prior experience working in gaming startup/company&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;New York City residents only: Minimum salary salary of $109,000/year + equity and benefits&lt;br&gt;*Note: Disclosure as required by NYC Pay Transparency Law&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Colorado residents only: Minimum salary of &lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:3,&amp;quot;3&amp;quot;:87200}&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:33562689,&amp;quot;3&amp;quot;:{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;\&amp;quot;$\&amp;quot;#,##0_);[Red]\\(\&amp;quot;$\&amp;quot;#,##0\\)&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;3&amp;quot;:1},&amp;quot;9&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;16&amp;quot;:11,&amp;quot;28&amp;quot;:1}&quot; data-sheets-formula=&quot;=R[0]C[-1]*0.8&quot;&gt;$87,200 &lt;/span&gt;/year + equity and benefits&lt;br&gt;*Note: Disclosure as required by sb19-085(8-5-20).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;diversityStatement-278s4F margin-top-20 textMedium-2-4rKJ textDefault-1mTLiI sizeMedium-2cmn1g lineLarge-2G0ms4 weightNormal-3CX1dN&quot;&gt;#buildbelonging #LI-KG1&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;Benefits and Perks&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;list-2wIoMU sizeMedium-3TgKSU weightNormal-sMrqnI lineLarge-2ze3kk&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Comprehensive medical insurance including Health, Dental and Vision (plus up to $20,000 for gender affirmation procedures)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Mental health resources and quarterly wellness stipends&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;16+ paid holidays, 4 weeks of PTO + use-what-you-need sick days&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Paid parental leave (plus fertility, adoption and other family planning benefits)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Flexible long-term work options (remote and hybrid)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Volunteer time off&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A diverse slate of Employee Resource Groups&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Plus commuter contributions and other perks for office-based employees&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;About Us&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Discord is a voice, video and text app that helps friends and communities come together to hang out and explore their interests — from artists and activists, to study groups, sneakerheads, plant parents, and more. With 150 million monthly users across 19 million active communities, called servers, Discord has grown to become one of the most popular communications services in the world. Discord was built without selling ads or user data and instead, offers a premium subscription called Nitro that gives users special perks like higher quality streams and fun customizations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We’re working toward an inclusive world where no one feels like an outsider, where genuine human connection is a click, text chat, or voice call away. A place where everyone can find belonging. Challenging? Heck yes. Rewarding? Double heck yes. It’s a mission that gives us the chance to positively impact millions of people all over the world. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;So if this strikes a chord with you, come build belonging with us!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Discord is looking for an experienced Creative Director to lead our creative team (Art School) composed of graphic designers, illustrators, motion designers, and copywriters. We&#39;re looking for someone who loves to inspire others, and find inspiration in the wonderfully diverse communities we welcome on Discord.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You&#39;ll be the guiding figure for our creative strategy and direction, ensuring our brand values come to life across a variety of mediums. As the Creative Director you&#39;ll oversee the delivery of all essential creative projects from ideation through execution while keeping the creatives of Art School engaged and inspired. Hint: a strong meme game helps.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;At Discord no interest is too niche, and no community is too full. We welcome those who reach toward the edges to find inspiration, shared experiences, and new friends. We are a fun, sometimes silly, and always collaborative team. We focus on creating the highest quality experiences that create belonging above all else.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;What you&#39;ll be doing&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;list-2wIoMU sizeMedium-3TgKSU weightNormal-sMrqnI lineLarge-2ze3kk&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Complement our existing art direction and brand identity with your strategic creative vision&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Motivate and inspire our creative team members to make a difference without micromanaging&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Create a culture of feedback that is healthy, supportive, and open&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Function as team advocate to provide a cohesive vision of Discord&#39;s identity in all audience facing respects&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Recruit and foster the career growth of designers, product illustrators, animators, and copywriters&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Work with the Product/Engineering and Marketing teams to ensure our creative pursuits reflect their goals and supporting their specific needs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You&#39;ll help define our employer brand and highlight what makes Discord a perfect place to do great design work&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;You’ll Thrive In This Role If…&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;list-2wIoMU sizeMedium-3TgKSU weightNormal-sMrqnI lineLarge-2ze3kk&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;5+ years of leading a creative team at an agency or in-house&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;10+ years experience in design or art direction&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Excellent ability to explain your creative vision and inspire others, but also solicit and listen to feedback&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You lead with passion and vision, and inspire others to deliver their best work while keeping them engaged and happy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Portfolio that shows your creativity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You are genuinely interested in furthering the careers of the members of your teams&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ability and desire to adapt to the changing landscape of technology&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience with events/conferences, digital media, apparel, and advertising&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Expertise in leading and managing a group of cross-disciplinary teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience motivating and positively engaging staff and management cross functionally in ways that build trust and enthusiasm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience hiring and scaling a team of varied skills for growth that&#39;s appropriate to the forecasted needs of the company&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;Bonus Points&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;list-2wIoMU sizeMedium-3TgKSU weightNormal-sMrqnI lineLarge-2ze3kk&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Familiar with 3D and 2D illustrators and the tools they use&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Familiar with Animators/Motion Designers and the tools they use&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge with reviewing and managing any outside agencies or freelancers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;New York City residents only: Minimum salary salary of $INSERT NYC &#39;MIN&#39;/year + equity and benefits\n*Note: Disclosure as required by NYC Pay Transparency Law\n\nColorado residents only: Minimum salary of $INSERT CO &#39;MIN&#39;/year + equity and benefits\n*Note: Disclosure as required by sb19-085(8-5-20).&amp;quot;}&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:33571329,&amp;quot;3&amp;quot;:{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:0},&amp;quot;12&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;17&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;28&amp;quot;:1}&quot; data-sheets-textstyleruns=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:0}{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:56,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:{&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:16711680},&amp;quot;6&amp;quot;:1}}{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:72,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:{&amp;quot;6&amp;quot;:1}}{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:73}{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:203,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:{&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:16711680},&amp;quot;6&amp;quot;:1}}{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:218}&quot;&gt;New York City residents only: Minimum salary of $209,000/year + equity and benefits&lt;br&gt;*Note: Disclosure as required by NYC Pay Transparency Law&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Colorado residents only: Minimum salary of $167,200 /year + equity and benefits&lt;br&gt;*Note: Disclosure as required by sb19-085(8-5-20)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;New York City residents only: Minimum salary salary of $INSERT NYC &#39;MIN&#39;/year + equity and benefits\n*Note: Disclosure as required by NYC Pay Transparency Law\n\nColorado residents only: Minimum salary of $INSERT CO &#39;MIN&#39;/year + equity and benefits\n*Note: Disclosure as required by sb19-085(8-5-20).&amp;quot;}&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:33571329,&amp;quot;3&amp;quot;:{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:0},&amp;quot;12&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;17&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;28&amp;quot;:1}&quot; data-sheets-textstyleruns=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:0}{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:56,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:{&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:16711680},&amp;quot;6&amp;quot;:1}}{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:72,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:{&amp;quot;6&amp;quot;:1}}{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:73}{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:203,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:{&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:16711680},&amp;quot;6&amp;quot;:1}}{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:218}&quot;&gt;#buildbelonging #LI-KS1 #LI-Remote&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;Benefits and Perks&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;list-2wIoMU sizeMedium-3TgKSU weightNormal-sMrqnI lineLarge-2ze3kk&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Comprehensive medical insurance including Health, Dental and Vision (plus up to $20,000 for gender affirmation procedures)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Mental health resources and quarterly wellness stipends&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;16+ paid holidays, 4 weeks of PTO + use-what-you-need sick days&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Paid parental leave (plus fertility, adoption and other family planning benefits)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Flexible long-term work options (remote and hybrid)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Volunteer time off&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A diverse slate of Employee Resource Groups&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Plus commuter contributions and other perks for office-based employees&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;About Us&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Discord is a voice, video and text app that helps friends and communities come together to hang out and explore their interests — from artists and activists, to study groups, sneakerheads, plant parents, and more. With 150 million monthly users across 19 million active communities, called servers, Discord has grown to become one of the most popular communications services in the world. Discord was built without selling ads or user data and instead, offers a premium subscription called Nitro that gives users special perks like higher quality streams and fun customizations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We’re working toward an inclusive world where no one feels like an outsider, where genuine human connection is a click, text chat, or voice call away. A place where everyone can find belonging. Challenging? Heck yes. Rewarding? Double heck yes. It’s a mission that gives us the chance to positively impact millions of people all over the world. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;So if this strikes a chord with you, come build belonging with us!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;People love Discord because it connects them with people they care about - friends, family, and communities with shared interests. Tens of millions of users use our world-class audio/video calling, text chat, and collaborative functionality like streaming to &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://blog.discord.com/talking-to-each-other-during-covid-19-6ca471fbe5ac&amp;amp;sa=D&amp;amp;source=docs&amp;amp;ust=1635975793350000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0SFbZdq6rCFZSUYHVEg25G&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;communicate every day&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;As a Manager in the Data Science department, you will coordinate with cross-functional partners like product managers and designers to leverage machine learning, causal inference, and analytics to guide development of innovative product features and ensure that Discord is the best service it can be. Check out our blog about how our team informs strategy &amp;amp; innovation at Discord &lt;a href=&quot;https://discord.com/blog/how-data-science-informs-strategy-innovation-at-discord&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;What You&#39;ll Be Doing&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;ul1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Partner closely with product, engineering, and business teams to understand feature adoption, proactively identify opportunities for improvement, and build robust scalable tools to empower decision-making at all levels of the company &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Create novel and interpretable metrics to provide insight into the health of the Discord app and use analytics, modeling, and experimentation to understand their impact on business goals&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Transform data into information - establish hypotheses, dig deep, and seek to understand root causes - to improve the effectiveness of our marketing efforts&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Own the vision and roadmap for a Data Science team, supporting a key pillar of Discord&#39;s mission&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Build and mentor a world-class analytics team, expanding the impact of data at Discord&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;In partnership with our Data leaders, inform architectural decisions, establish best practices, develop lean scalable processes, and contribute to the overall direction of the Data organization at Discord!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;You Will Thrive In This Role If&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;ul1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;3+ years of leadership experience as a people manager, leading a team of 3+ data scientists. Ideally, your team would have had technical expertise covering at least two of the following: BI &amp;amp; analytics, machine learning, and A/B experimentation&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Excellent skills in communicating to both technical and non-technical audiences, with an ability to explain complex concepts in easy-to-understand ways&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;6+ years of industry experience in applying machine learning and/or analytics techniques to answer vague and challenging business problems&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Proficient in Python/R or SQL (any dialect) for hands-on modeling and/or analysis&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Familiarity with A/B testing principles&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A collaborative attitude and natural curiosity&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Points&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience with social media or within digital consumer products&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Proficient in modern BI tooling (Chartio, Looker, Tableau, etc.), with an eye towards clear, rich visualizations and performance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience with very large data sets and distributed computing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Familiarity with Airflow, GCP, BigQuery&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience partnering with business teams in a data-driven culture&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Passion for Discord or online communities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;#buildbelonging&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
