&lt;h2&gt;Discord is looking for a highly technical, hands-on, and mission-driven Engineering Manager to build and lead a Developer Productivity team. As the manager responsible for a Developer Productivity team reporting into the Foundation Department, you will have enormous impact by working directly with engineering teams and departments to remove friction and generate compounding leverage.&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;This team&#39;s mission is provide dependable tools — effective primitives that empower engineering teams to accelerate development and delivery. If you are motivated by building developer tools, working with internal engineering teams, have a passion for seeing others succeed, and lead with empathy in everything you do, then read on!&lt;/h2&gt;
