&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have 5+ years of experience as a Software Engineer working in the developer productivity space&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have 2+ years of experience as an Engineering Manager and successfully managed a team of 3+ Software Engineers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are comfortable with many languages such as Python, Rust, Elixir, TS/JS and have a pulse on the surrounding language tooling ecosystems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience working with many teams and stakeholders and have a track record of elegantly managing and communicating change&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are comfortable writing the roadmap -- not just following one&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are passionate about coaching and leading other engineers, but love to code when the opportunity arises&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You get to the heart of issues and lead your team to come up with effective solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Points&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
