&lt;h2&gt;At the heart of Discord&#39;s communities are our users who talk and hang out in them every day. The Activities group unlocks infinite activities inside Discord, from music and games to events and beyond.&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Discord is looking for a technical, creative, hands-on, and mission-focused Engineering Manager to join the Activities Studio team. You will oversee engineers building games and activities used by millions across Discord.&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop the careers of the engineers through coaching and finding opportunities that support their technical skillset and goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use your technical expertise to constantly improve and ensure your team achieves extraordinary results at the high technical level we set.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop insights into issues slowing down the team and develop processes and workflows to allow the team to achieve its goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build engaged teams by coaching, and instilling influence in your engineers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with the Activities Studio disciplines from game design, art, animation, production and QA to achieve the best games and activity experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
