&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;About Us&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Discord is a voice, video and text app that helps friends and communities come together to hang out and explore their interests — from artists and activists, to study groups, sneakerheads, plant parents, and more. With 150 million monthly users across 19 million active communities, called servers, Discord has grown to become one of the most popular communications services in the world. Discord was built without selling ads or user data and instead, offers a premium subscription called Nitro that gives users special perks like higher quality streams and fun customizations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We’re working toward an inclusive world where no one feels like an outsider, where genuine human connection is a click, text chat, or voice call away. A place where everyone can find belonging. Challenging? Heck yes. Rewarding? Double heck yes. It’s a mission that gives us the chance to positively impact millions of people all over the world. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;So if this strikes a chord with you, come build belonging with us!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;Discord is your place to talk. Whether you&#39;re part of a school club, gaming group, worldwide art community, or just a handful of friends that want to spend time together, millions of people use Discord every day to create connections, hang out, and talk.&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;At the heart of Discord&#39;s communities is Safety. The Safety team at Discord ensures users find belonging by minimizing exposure to spam and other forms of platform abuse. We are excited to find others passionate about making sure Discord is a safe and welcoming place for our users and hope you can join us on this mission.&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;As an Exploitative Content Lead, you will report to the Director of Trust and Safety and you will have a meaningful understanding of the abuse space while managing a team of dedicated specialists.&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;What you&#39;ll be doing&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Protect and serve our communities by managing and scaling our Exploitative Content team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize deep subject matter expertise and quantitative and qualitative methods to identify gaps across teams, develop root cause analyses, and enact continuous improvements in response to changing circumstances&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee sensitive projects from initial conception through implementation across multiple areas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with Policy, Product, Engineering, and Trust &amp;amp; Safety teams in the development of operational policies, tools, and solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with external partners to represent the Trust &amp;amp; Safety organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate and present to leadership on important initiatives and metrics for your team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;What you should have&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years work experience with building and leading teams, and experience in user safety and/or integrity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong people management skills––you&#39;re passionate and knowledgeable when it comes to developing your direct reports, and are excited to grow a world-class organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analytical backbone––you eagerly gather and present data to inform decisions and the ongoing tracking of success metrics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic problem solving––you&#39;re excited to find opportunities for improvement, and you&#39;re motivated to lead initiatives from start to finish&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong stakeholder management skills––you know how to leverage the skills of multiple disparate teams, including improving processes you don&#39;t directly own&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort with ambiguity––in ever-evolving situations, you approach initiatives with positivity and lead your team successfully through their completion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;Bonus Points&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Master&#39;s degree in a related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Six Sigma Certification&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with Discord&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multilingual&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;New York City residents only: Minimum salary of $130,000/year + equity and benefits*Note: Disclosure as required by NYC Pay Transparency Law&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Colorado residents only: Minimum salary of $104,000/year + equity and benefits*Note: Disclosure as required by sb19-085(8-5-20).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;Benefits and Perks&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;list-2wIoMU sizeMedium-3TgKSU weightNormal-sMrqnI lineLarge-2ze3kk&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Comprehensive medical insurance including Health, Dental and Vision (plus up to $20,000 for gender affirmation procedures)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Mental health resources and quarterly wellness stipends&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;16+ paid holidays, 4 weeks of PTO + use-what-you-need sick days&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Paid parental leave (plus fertility, adoption and other family planning benefits)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Flexible long-term work options (remote and hybrid)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Volunteer time off&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A diverse slate of Employee Resource Groups&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Plus commuter contributions and other perks for office-based employees&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;About Us&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Discord is a voice, video and text app that helps friends and communities come together to hang out and explore their interests — from artists and activists, to study groups, sneakerheads, plant parents, and more. With 150 million monthly users across 19 million active communities, called servers, Discord has grown to become one of the most popular communications services in the world. Discord was built without selling ads or user data and instead, offers a premium subscription called Nitro that gives users special perks like higher quality streams and fun customizations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We’re working toward an inclusive world where no one feels like an outsider, where genuine human connection is a click, text chat, or voice call away. A place where everyone can find belonging. Challenging? Heck yes. Rewarding? Double heck yes. It’s a mission that gives us the chance to positively impact millions of people all over the world. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;So if this strikes a chord with you, come build belonging with us!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Discord is on a mission to help everyone find belonging by creating a new kind of communications service that puts users first, is built with integrity, and improves the lives of the people and communities it serves.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;What started as a place for people to hang out while playing games together online has become so much more. From artists connecting with fans to students collaborating in real-time and young entrepreneurs inventing the future - there has never been a more exciting time to join.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Serving as a member of the global communications leadership team, this newly created role will be responsible for overseeing all communications efforts related to government relations and regulatory matters worldwide; our global platform, product and public policies including community guidelines; and a wide range of safety-related initiatives and programs. To be successful in this role, you have a deep understanding of the global political and regulatory landscape (from the US to the EU and beyond); have experience with elections, policy hearings and crisis management; and possess strong, trusted relationships with government-beat and policy-related reporters.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You will work with stakeholders across engineering, product design, public policy, regulation, safety, and legal. This role reports directly to our global head of communications and will work closely with our head of international communications and policy leader as we expand our business around the world.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;What You’ll Be Doing&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Lead policy communications strategy and planning globally as well as execute proactive communications campaigns&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Shape our policy narratives and communicate our public positions on complex, sensitive issues related to the intersection of technology, content, society and regulation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Advise senior leadership and cross-functional partners for policy-related thought leadership and crisis management&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Partner with our policy and safety teams on key initiatives to support teen safety and belonging&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Build and manage a team of policy communications managers and/or network of agency partnerships around the world&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Own key policy-related media relationships, provide guidance to reporters, and manage press queries/reactive communications about Discord’s platform/product/public policies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;You Will Thrive In This Role If..&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A passion for Discord and our mission&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;12+ years experience (combination of in-house, agency, government or NGO) building and scaling policy communications initiatives in the US, EU and around the world&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;5+ years experience managing teams and agency partners in multiple markets&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Knowledge and familiarity with US, EU, and other regional policy frameworks, from elections to regulation, with a global perspective&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Strong background in consumer technology and/or emerging categories, with established policy media relationships&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Operate with empathy and flexibility in a hybrid, collaborative and fast-paced environment with colleagues in various time zones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Effective prioritization when it comes to project management, navigating time-sensitive projects while maintaining quality on other important workstreams &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Bonus Points:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Fluent in two or more languages&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;An understanding of and/or experience using Discord&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
