&lt;h2 class=&quot;margin-top-20 textMedium-1BFntw textDefault-1wTgq3 sizeMedium-3TgKSU lineLarge-2ze3kk weightNormal-sMrqnI&quot;&gt;As a Payments and Fraud Manager, you have a knack for identifying fraud vectors and detecting high risk patterns of behavior. Reporting to our Manager of Operations Support, you will help build and manage brand new payments processes while growing our small but mighty fraud team. You lead by example, and aren&#39;t afraid to jump into the trenches for a good ol&#39; fashioned queue slay.&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;What you&#39;ll be doing&lt;/h4&gt;
