&lt;li&gt;BA/BS or equivalent work experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of experience in Payment Operations, Fraud Operations or an equivalent field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of team lead or management experience&lt;/li&gt;
