&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The People Operations team plays a critical role at the center of Discord, building out the infrastructure and tools that enable global operations and efficiency across our rapidly growing organization.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;People Services is a subteam of People Operations, serving as the nucleus of the organization’s operations by maintaining a high level of data integrity, serving as the first point of contact for employee and business partner inquiries and serving as key partners in critical cross-functional processes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;What You&#39;ll Be Doing&lt;/h4&gt;
