&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Serve as first responder to employee inquiries related to benefits, enrollments, payroll, company policies, verifications of employment, etc. in accordance with SLA standards; triage and/or escalate tickets to partner teams as needed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Partner closely with Payroll, Finance and Accounting to process payroll checklist activities in a timely manner every pay period&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Complete requests for reports from key cross-functional teams; partner with People Systems to identify opportunities for technology automation and collaborate on solutions to increase efficiency and self-service where appropriate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Partner closely with People Partners to provide POps support in service of their client groups&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Develop and regularly maintain internal knowledge base articles and resources to empower employees to be self-directed and successful&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Organize and maintain internal records and documentation and perform regular audits to ensure accuracy and completeness&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
