&lt;h2 class=&quot;margin-top-20 textMedium-1BFntw textDefault-1wTgq3 sizeMedium-3TgKSU lineLarge-2ze3kk weightNormal-sMrqnI&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for a Product Designer to embed within our Premium Products design team to build experiences that engage our users and achieve our mission of creating belonging.&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;margin-top-20 textMedium-1BFntw textDefault-1wTgq3 sizeMedium-3TgKSU lineLarge-2ze3kk weightNormal-sMrqnI&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;margin-top-20 textMedium-1BFntw textDefault-1wTgq3 sizeMedium-3TgKSU lineLarge-2ze3kk weightNormal-sMrqnI&quot;&gt;As a product designer, you&#39;ll be involved with the full product development process from end-to-end, from brainstorming to launch. You&#39;ll use a balance of product, interaction, and visual design skills within the area of Discord that you will end up building. If you&#39;re interested in joining a passionate team of designers that are designing features that will be used by millions of people across the world, come help us do that.&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;What you&#39;ll be doing&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;list-2wIoMU sizeMedium-3TgKSU weightNormal-sMrqnI lineLarge-2ze3kk&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You will report to our growing Product Design team within the Engineering, Product, Analytics and Design (EPAD) organization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Embed within a Premium Products squad and partner with engineers, product managers and data scientists to oversee the user experience of a Premium product from concept to launch — and then continue to improve it after it releases to millions of users&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Mix your visual, UX, and interaction design skills to design valuable features for our users.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Understand our goals and connect them with design decisions that can be articulated in individual or group settings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Foster a culture of design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;What you should have&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;list-2wIoMU sizeMedium-3TgKSU weightNormal-sMrqnI lineLarge-2ze3kk&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Minimum of 2 years experience designing and shipping a web/app product for a variety of devices and platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Product thinking and vision. You&#39;re more concerned with the &quot;why&quot; than the &quot;how&quot;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Excitement to dig into experiment data to help inform design iterations and whether something should ship&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A high level of craft&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience with Figma or Sketch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;Bonus Points&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;list-2wIoMU sizeMedium-3TgKSU weightNormal-sMrqnI lineLarge-2ze3kk&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience or willingness to mentor other designers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience building design systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Interface animation know-how&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;CSS, JavaScript, or React skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
