&lt;div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Discord is looking for a highly creative, hands-on and mission-driven Product Design Manager to lead product designers whose work helps our communities be as successful as possible.&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Your role will be to manage, hire and inspire a growing team of passionate designers that have a meaningful impact at Discord. You&#39;ll help the team put the user first, coaching designers through our process, and focusing the team on the highest impact problems with the best solutions. You will be an essential member of design leadership. You thrive on collaborating and take great enjoyment in working to improve people, product, and process.&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;What you&#39;ll be doing&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;list-2wIoMU sizeMedium-3TgKSU weightNormal-sMrqnI lineLarge-2ze3kk&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop a team of highly-engaged designers by coaching and instilling a sense of ownership and impact. Provide direction and guidance of product designers&#39; output, promote partnerships and design process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&#39;ll build close bonds with your corresponding engineering and product management leaders to influence product strategy and ensure world-class product execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply your technical expertise to constantly raise the bar and ensure your team achieves extraordinary results at the [high technical level we set](https://discord.com/category/engineering).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adjust team composition and eventually creating new teams to adapt to changing needs or tuning team dynamics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Make sound first-principle decisions around resourcing, and making the rationale clear to partners and team members.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with other design leaders to continuously improve the Design organization and uphold our &lt;a href=&quot;https://discord.com/blog/the-four-values-of-working-at-discord&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;workplace philosophy&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Engineering to develop core component frameworks and best-practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Occasionally you will be hands-on with the design work, pitching in from time to time in order to support your team and keep them focused on deeper work — however this is primarily a management role (especially as the team grows larger).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;What you should have&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;list-2wIoMU sizeMedium-3TgKSU weightNormal-sMrqnI lineLarge-2ze3kk&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have 2+ years of experience as a Design Manager and/or have led at least 2 Product Designers previously within a design team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6+ years experience in multi-platform digital products as a Product Designer (or similar role). Especially fluent with mobile product development and consumer products, with experience using prototyping tools to demonstrate product concepts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A portfolio of work you&#39;ve designed and shipped as well as examples of work you directed delivered by your team. Examples of how you have previously influenced your product teams, organizations or discipline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An enjoyment of people leadership. This includes recruiting, training and developing, organization design, and leading by example.&lt;br&gt;You thrive in ambiguous environments and get excited about figuring out strategies or processes to address them — both in product and internal team structures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong eye for craft. You can identify when work can benefit from more time or investment, identifying gaps in visual or interaction design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;History of strong partnerships with engineering and product management leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are a first principles thinker that can work with others to come up with pragmatic solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Designing yourself does not scare you, and you’re happy to jump in to help if needed. You are still a designer even if you don&#39;t do it all the time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You keep up with the industry trends and can assess new tools and techniques.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;diversityStatement-278s4F margin-top-20 textMedium-2-4rKJ textDefault-1mTLiI sizeMedium-2cmn1g lineLarge-2G0ms4 weightNormal-3CX1dN&quot;&gt;#buildbelonging #LI-SC1&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;New York City residents only: Minimum salary of &lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:3,&amp;quot;3&amp;quot;:158000}&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:33563201,&amp;quot;3&amp;quot;:{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;\&amp;quot;$\&amp;quot;#,##0&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;3&amp;quot;:1},&amp;quot;9&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;12&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;16&amp;quot;:11,&amp;quot;28&amp;quot;:1}&quot;&gt;$158,000&lt;/span&gt;/year + equity and benefits&lt;br&gt;*Note: Disclosure as required by NYC Pay Transparency Law&lt;/p&gt;
