&lt;li&gt;4+ years of experience building performant dashboards using Tableau, Looker, or a similar software - with proficiency in designing clean crisp visualizations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years acting as a strategic thought leader with partner teams, helping define success metrics, set targets, and design proactive analyses that help the team achieve its goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years of experience in the design, analysis, and interpretation of A/B tests in a large data environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills, with the ability to translate complicated findings or technical approaches in easy-to-understand ways&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A desire to work in a fast-paced environment with many unsolved problems!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Last but not least - a collaborative attitude and a healthy dose of natural curiosity!&lt;/li&gt;
