&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You are good at solving problems and you use data to understand trends and develop recommendations for action&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Meaningful relationships are your thing. You excel at making a connection with those around you and across all levels of the organization&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You are told that your proactiveness and flexible style are what makes you a great partner and collaborator&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
