&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Comprehensive medical insurance including Health, Dental and Vision (plus up to $20,000 for gender affirmation procedures)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
