&lt;li&gt;Design, build, and support Discord&#39;s next generation experimentation platform - specifically, our configuration tooling and UX.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with external (sometimes non-technical) stakeholders and customers throughout the company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand and influence product telemetry practices to support experimentation needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;You&#39;ll Thrive in This Role If...&lt;/h4&gt;
