&lt;li&gt;5+ years work experience in building and leading large teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;First-rate leadership skills––you&#39;re passionate about developing and growing world-class organizations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analytical backbone––you eagerly gather and present data to inform decisions and the ongoing tracking of success metrics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic problem solving––you&#39;re excited to find opportunities for improvement, and you&#39;re motivated to lead projects from start to finish&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner management skills––you know how to build relationships and leverage the skills of multiple teams, including improving processes you don&#39;t directly own&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort with ambiguity––in ever-evolving situations, you approach initiatives with positivity and lead your team(s) through their completion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
