&lt;li&gt;MBA or master&#39;s degree in a related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Six Sigma Certification&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in management consulting, business analysis or related roles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience leading online safety and/or responsible innovation teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
