&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Creating and maintaining internal libraries and documentation around our design system, enforcing these principles when applicable across the larger product organization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Working with our engineering team to develop custom Figma and internal tooling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Contribute ideas and strategies along with engineering and the larger design org to further the future of design systems at Discord.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Create high-quality mocks and interactive prototypes to demonstrate your work. Use research and data to inform your priorities and approach.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Collaborate with designers and engineers across the company to identify needs, and communication problems to solve within the design system.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Comfortable communicating and presenting to groups, sharing often for input and feedback across the design org.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Passionate about innovating on current norms, not accepting the status quo as gospel but questioning better techniques or approaches.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
