&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Minimum of 4 years in experience design, with fluency across web, mobile and gestural interaction design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Multiple years of experience working with embedded design systems teams, building close relationships with Engineering and other partners to craft innovative design languages and tooling to up-level our company’s product quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Sharp eye for detail. High level of craft and attention to detail, with exceptional visual and interaction finesse in all of your work. You leave no stone unturned in your deliverables.&lt;/li&gt;
