&lt;h3&gt;What we look for&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;You have 6+ years of experience as a Software Engineer.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;You have product sense, maintain a high degree of empathy for your internal and external users and seek feedback from them about your work&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;You approach problems with first principles. You get excited about working collaboratively to figure out solutions to complex problems, and then working on them.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
