&lt;div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;The Data Infrastructure team builds data pipelines to reliably collect, anonymize, and process billions of product activity events every day. We operate a petabyte-scale data warehouse and provide tools that empower the machine learning, data science, and business analysis teams at Discord. Our work enables user privacy and product features; and is foundational to making Discord a safer place to talk and hang out with your friends.&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;If that sounds exciting to you, read on!&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;margin-top-40 margin-bottom-8 textH4-3Bngsz headingDefault-2s3GxE sizeLarge-2FUtr2 lineTiny-1v9oiX weightSemiBold-19z6Hb&quot;&gt;What You&#39;ll Be Doing&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;list-2wIoMU sizeMedium-3TgKSU weightNormal-sMrqnI lineLarge-2ze3kk&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build the platform that empowers our Data Science, Machine Learning, powers product features used by millions of users every day.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and operate our entire data stack using modern technologies such as BigQuery, Cassandra, Apache Beam, Pub/Sub, and Airflow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build efficient solutions on top of Google Cloud Platform using Python and Scala.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
